{
  "id": "adv_bond_hrk_01_05",
  "title": "佐伯遙子5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふふ～ん。おかえりなさ～い、こころちゃん\n今日は学校どうだった？　楽しかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm-hmm~ Welcome back‚ Kokoro-chan!\nHow was school today? Did you have fun?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1400.0000000000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ただいまですー。別にいつも通りですよ\n突然親戚みたいなこと聞いてきてどうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm home~ Nothing special‚ same as always\nWhy are you suddenly asking me things like a relative?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……そうよね。ごめんなさい\n特に深い意味はないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… You're right. Sorry about that.\nI didn't mean anything deep by it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃんの制服姿を見る機会ってあんまりないから\nふと学校ではどうしてるのかな～って思っただけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't get many chances to see you in your uniform‚\nso I just wondered what you're like at school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "こころが制服を着ている時に遙子さんと会って\nいないだけで、こころはちゃんと学校に行ってますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just that we don't meet while I'm wearing it‚\nbut I do go to school properly‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かってるわよ。あー、こころちゃんを見ていたら\n私も学生時代が懐かしくなってきたわね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I know that. Ah~ Seeing you makes me feel\nso nostalgic for my own student days~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "（学校のことはあまり聞かれたくないのかしら？）\n（ただの雑談のつもりだったのに悪いことをしちゃったわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Maybe she doesn't want to talk about school?）\n（I meant it as small talk‚ but I might have been rude.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "こころはあんまり学校好きじゃないです～\nみーんな同じ格好で同じことして、何の意味があるのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't really like school that much~\nEveryone dressed the same‚ doing the same things… What's the point?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころちゃん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kokoro-chan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "なーんて、嘘ですよ！　制服は可愛くてお気に入りです\n遙子さんの通ってた学校はどんな制服だったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just kidding! I actually love my uniform because it's cute.\nWhat kind of uniform did your school have‚ Haruko-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "星見高校だったから、琴乃ちゃん達と同じセーラー服よ\n数年前までピチピチのJKだったんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was Hoshimi High‚ so the same sailor suit as Kotono and the others.\nI was a fresh high school girl just a few years ago!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6999974569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ほ～、遙子さんにも本当の『佐伯遙子十七歳』の時期が\nあったんですね～。なんだか感慨深いです～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh~ So Haruko-san really did have a\n\"Haruko Saeki‚ Age 17\" period. I'm quite moved!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.933325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "悪気がないのは分かるけど、遙子もちょっぴり傷付くわ\nまだギリ十七歳に見えないことも……なくないかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you don't mean any harm‚ but that hurts a little.\nDon't I still look 17‚ just barely… or maybe not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0999923707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "ふーむ……どうでしょう……見えないことも……\nそれなら試してみましょう！　レッツ、お着替えです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… let's see… Maybe you could…\nThen let's test it! Time for a dress-up session!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7666590374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.8833297731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "あの～こころが無茶振りしちゃったのが悪いんですけど\n遙子さん、大丈夫です？　入らないなら無理せず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um~ It's my fault for pushing this on you‚ but\nare you okay‚ Haruko-san? Don't force it if it doesn't fit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9333297731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.1333216351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "ぜ、全然大丈夫よ！　入るわ！　いえ……\n入るか、入らないかじゃない。入れるのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm perfectly fine! It fits! No…\nIt's not about \"fitting.\" I'm making it fit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1333216351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 149.9999888103
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 152.5666625977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "くっ……もう少しでホックが締まりそうなの……！\nあと……少しで……頑張るのよ、遙子！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… The hook is so close to closing…!\nJust… a bit… more… Hang in there‚ Haruko!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6666366579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 159.099969993
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 167.4666183474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "こころもお手伝いします！　遙子さん、息を止めて！\nもっとグッとお腹に力を入れて、引っ込めるのです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll help you! Haruko-san‚ hold your breath!\nTighten your stomach and pull it in more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4666183474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 176.0666183474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "せーの、で息を止めてください。一緒にホックを\n締めましょう！　いきますよ～、せーのっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On the count of three‚ hold your breath. Let's close\nthe hook together! Ready~ and‚ go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.0666183474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 184.2999516807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "ふんぬっ！！！！！！！！！！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "HNNNNGGHHHH!!!!!!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.2999516807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 186.266616313
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "は、入った～！　入ったわ！　スカートが入った！\nふふんっ、どう？　これが佐伯遙子二十歳の実力よ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-It's on~! It fits! The skirt finally fits!\nHehe‚ how's that? This is the power of Haruko Saeki‚ age 20!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.266616313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 193.1666550477
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 196.5666549683
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 200.1332829796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "おおっ、さすがピチピチの二十歳です！\n先輩の頑張りにこころの胸も熱くなりました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohh‚ as expected of a fresh 20-year-old!\nSenior's hard work has touched Kokoro's heart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.1332829796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 208.6999496463
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_05-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "こころも来るべき『赤崎こころ二十歳』に向けて\n日々の鍛錬を怠らないように頑張りま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll work hard for my own \"Kokoro Akazaki‚ age 20\"\nand won't skip my daily training~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.6999496463,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}